39:58.188 --> 40:00.731
No, I mean, the getting punched
in the face part sucked, right?

40:00.815 --> 40:03.901
The getting taken care of
after the punch, it was nice.

40:03.985 --> 40:06.320
Florence Nightingale syndrome.

40:07.489 --> 40:09.990
