40:25.715 --> 40:27.132
- Let's go deep.
- I like it.

40:28.218 --> 40:29.718
Why do they always forget my bacon?

40:29.844 --> 40:32.346
I can't believe
you got that guy knocked out.

40:32.472 --> 40:34.598
