unconscious man, ever.

40:40.355 --> 40:44.066
Are you dating him,
or are you contemplating adoption?

40:45.193 --> 40:48.529
Andie, I am loving your notes
on this piece.

40:51.366 --> 40:52.449
Thank you, Lana.

40:52.534 --> 40:55.160
- When are you seeing him again?
- Tonight.

40:56.037 --> 40:58.205
He's invited me over for dinner.

40:58.331 --> 41:01.959
Marvelous.
I've got a feeling about this one.

41:02.043 --> 41:03.961
