and tipoff in about eight.

41:51.843 --> 41:54.052
Great. I'm starving.

42:06.107 --> 42:10.944
Oh, so perfectly pink!

42:31.633 --> 42:36.303
Sheryl, Tori, Sinead,
Jewel, Fiona, Carly.

42:36.429 --> 42:40.140
- The gang's all here!
- Great!

42:41.601 --> 42:43.477
