44:09.939 --> 44:12.858
Wait, wait. Hey. Hey. You okay?

44:13.901 --> 44:15.485
It's beautiful.

44:18.156 --> 44:20.198
- Thanks.
- You're beautiful,

44:20.283 --> 44:22.409
the game, the whole thing.

44:24.746 --> 44:26.580
