- Post. Post.

46:43.134 --> 46:45.010
Reverse!

46:46.095 --> 46:49.306
- There we go, baby.
- I can't believe he missed that shot.

46:49.390 --> 46:52.476
Take it! Take it! Hit it!

46:52.560 --> 46:54.060
No!

46:54.145 --> 46:57.439
How the hell did you know
he was gonna miss that shot?

46:58.024 --> 47:01.651
