from the top of the key.

47:01.736 --> 47:04.488
That's the way it ended as the Knicks
could not get off another shot.

47:06.324 --> 47:08.200
Oh, man.

47:10.495 --> 47:13.580
Houston never misses
from the top of the key.

47:24.675 --> 47:27.802
Does Princess Sophia
wanna come out and play?

47:28.513 --> 47:30.972
