47:33.851 --> 47:39.105
No, no, no, no, no, no!
Wait, wait. You're kidding me, right?

47:39.190 --> 47:41.441
- Princess Sophia?
- Little, big. Little, big.

47:41.526 --> 47:43.902
I don't know. We will find out.

47:44.654 --> 47:46.905
You know, hang on a second.

47:48.658 --> 47:52.410
All right, listen, you can't name
my member Princess Sophia.

47:52.495 --> 47:54.329
- It doesn't...
- Yes, I can.

47:54.413 --> 47:58.208
Listen to me. If you're gonna
name my member, all right,

47:58.292 --> 48:00.794
you gotta name it
something hyper-masculine, okay?

48:00.878 --> 48:02.462
Something like Spike or Butch

48:02.547 --> 48:05.048
or Krull, the Warrior King,
but not Princess Sophia.

48:05.132 --> 48:06.758
What did you just say?

48:08.010 --> 48:10.262
Spike. You know what I mean?

48:10.346 --> 48:13.139
- No, no, after Spike.
- Butch.

48:13.224 --> 48:14.849
After Butch.

48:18.062 --> 48:20.438
Krull, the Warrior King.

48:20.523 --> 48:25.485
Does Krull, the Warrior King
want to come out and play?

48:27.905 --> 48:30.740
- No.
- Come on out of there.

48:31.367 --> 48:33.868
- Krull!
- You know what?

48:35.246 --> 48:37.664
Due to intense humiliation,

48:37.748 --> 48:42.544
the king has momentarily
abdicated his throne, okay?

48:44.422 --> 48:46.923
- Yeah.
- Well, in that case,

48:48.342 --> 48:50.135
I better get going.

48:54.181 --> 48:56.308
Take care of our love fern, honey.

49:14.201 --> 49:15.452
Hi.

49:16.954 --> 49:18.872
Can I see you tomorrow?

49:18.956 --> 49:21.249
- Really?
- I hope so.

49:23.669 --> 49:24.836
- Call me.
- I will.

49:24.920 --> 49:26.963
- And I'll call you.
- Sweet dreams.

49:27.048 --> 49:28.715
