51:01.600 --> 51:04.227
No kidding. A Chinese Crested.

51:04.311 --> 51:06.479
So, it's like a dog, right?

51:06.605 --> 51:09.733
- Whoa! There he is.
- Ben. Ben.

51:09.817 --> 51:11.401
You're hurting Krull's feelings.

51:11.485 --> 51:14.738
- Krull, is it?
- Krull. Krull, the Warrior king.

51:14.822 --> 51:16.906
Well, sure, 'cause that's clearly what...

51:16.991 --> 51:19.159
Oh, wait. There's more.

51:19.285 --> 51:20.994
- What do you got there?
- Oh, nice.

51:21.078 --> 51:23.663
- For me? Get out of town.
- Try it on.

51:23.748 --> 51:26.166
- Looks like the inside of a raincoat.
- Matches!

51:26.250 --> 51:27.667
Oh, yeah,
that's gonna fit nicely, sweetie.

51:27.793 --> 51:29.169
- Try it on.
- Thank you.

51:29.295 --> 51:30.503
No, Ben, put it on.

51:30.629 --> 51:33.506
No, you should try it on, otherwise
you don't know if it's gonna fit.

51:33.632 --> 51:35.675
- Go for it.
- Manners never hurt anybody.

51:35.801 --> 51:37.761
I was just gonna save it
for a special occasion.

51:37.845 --> 51:39.804
All right. Check that out.

51:40.639 --> 51:42.265
Oh, yeah, that's nice.

51:42.349 --> 51:43.767
Hey.

51:43.851 --> 51:46.144
You're a vision in khaki.

51:47.688 --> 51:52.442
It's gonna be a happy little family,
just the three of us.

51:52.526 --> 51:54.611
We are, aren't we?

51:54.695 --> 51:57.197
- Wow.
- He's our boy, Ben.

51:57.281 --> 51:59.199
Oh, see, that's sweet.

52:02.870 --> 52:06.956
Hey, hey, hey, Andie.
It is good to see you, too, sweetie.

52:07.041 --> 52:09.459
