52:42.409 --> 52:44.369
Oh, come here.

52:45.246 --> 52:48.081
- Do you love him?
- Oh, I do.

52:48.749 --> 52:50.667
Oh, look at Krull's necklace.

52:50.751 --> 52:53.002
He's got more ice than Liberace,
don't you?

52:53.087 --> 52:55.213
Oh, it's just a little frosting.

52:58.592 --> 53:00.552
- Frosting?
- Frosting.

53:01.929 --> 53:04.889
We were thinking bold, new, fresh.

53:05.266 --> 53:06.933
Frost yourself.

53:07.685 --> 53:09.853
- Excuse me?
- Frost yourself.

53:09.937 --> 53:11.938
- The slogan for the campaign.
- You frost a cake.

53:12.022 --> 53:13.356
We're in the middle
of a meeting, Benjamin.

53:13.440 --> 53:15.775
I'm talking about diamonds.
They're frosting.

53:15.901 --> 53:19.195
As in, "Whoa,
would you check out her frosting. "

53:19.280 --> 53:20.446
Frost yourself.

53:20.573 --> 53:22.031
- Frost yourself.
- How did you come up with it?

53:22.116 --> 53:25.285
I got it off the woman
who's falling madly in love with me.

53:25.411 --> 53:27.704
It may have possibilities,
but as far as the woman

53:27.788 --> 53:31.207
who's falling madly in love with you,
I will decide that at the party.

53:31.292 --> 53:33.042
- If he can get her there.
- Now just think about it.

53:33.127 --> 53:37.255
- Ladies, frost yourself.
- Frost yourself.

53:37.715 --> 53:39.132
We can introduce it at the party.

53:39.216 --> 53:40.550
- It should be the theme.
- Yes.

53:40.634 --> 53:42.135
- Everything frosted.
- All of it.

53:42.219 --> 53:44.554
- Martini glasses.
- Chandeliers.

53:44.638 --> 53:46.472
- Jewels everywhere.
- The women.

53:46.557 --> 53:50.602
- The whole party, a sparkling diamond.
- All of it frosted.

53:53.147 --> 53:56.232
Women of New York, frost yourselves!

53:56.317 --> 53:59.986
- Hey, frost this!
- Well, I like it.

54:04.909 --> 54:07.744
Yeah, yeah, yeah, I hear you.

54:07.828 --> 54:10.747
You have 17 new messages.

54:10.831 --> 54:14.334
