54:20.633 --> 54:23.593
Benny, it's Andie.
Guess you're not home.

54:23.677 --> 54:26.095
Three, received at 5:48.

54:26.180 --> 54:28.431
Benny bear,
are you not answering your phone?

54:28.515 --> 54:32.518
- Yes, I am.
