54:32.603 --> 54:35.688
Hey, buddy. Game three tonight.
Blondie's. Don't be late. I will kill you.

54:35.814 --> 54:37.315
- Who is it?
- It's me.

54:37.399 --> 54:41.319
- Five, received at 5:52.
- It's me.

54:45.574 --> 54:47.825
- What a surprise.
- I've been trying to get a hold of you.

54:47.910 --> 54:51.037
- Yeah?
- I did something kind of wacky.

54:52.247 --> 54:53.665
- Yeah?
- Yes.

54:53.749 --> 54:57.293
I used Photoshop at work today
to composite our faces together

54:57.378 --> 54:59.462
to see what our kids would look like.

54:59.546 --> 55:01.381
"Our family album. "

55:14.853 --> 55:17.271
You don't wanna see our children?

55:17.731 --> 55:21.067
We don't have children.

55:33.414 --> 55:34.956
