55:37.084 --> 55:40.878
You know what? I'm sorry. No, no, no.
I didn't mean it like that.

55:40.963 --> 55:43.506
All right? Show me, show me,
show me, show me.

55:43.590 --> 55:46.259
- Please show me.
- "We don't have children!"

55:46.385 --> 55:50.054
No, I thought you meant Krull.
I just wanted...

55:50.139 --> 55:52.640
- Will you show them to me?
- You don't wanna see them.

55:52.766 --> 55:54.350
I do. Please.

55:54.435 --> 55:58.104
Please show them to me.
I really do wanna see them.

55:58.230 --> 55:59.564
Really?

56:00.649 --> 56:02.233
